Title: What will Penguicon look like in 2020?
Book Description: Birds of a feather: let's get together to talk about the future of Penguicon. What will it look like in 2020? Your autonomous- electric car drops you off at the convention and you are automatically registered- with payment taken from your Penguicash account. Then what? Does hospitality have a list of you favorite foods that are dropped in by drone? Is a custom costume cut for you based on prior appearances and the movies you attended that year? Let's use our scifi interest to tell the future.
